936
00:39:20,090 --> 00:39:22,010
Of course I'll teach him.

937
00:39:22,150 --> 00:39:23,360
But you need to understand.

938
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,390
Not every student

939
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,440
can be taught well in school.

940
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:29,400
